  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 - \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One dies in Nainadive - relatives blame hospital staff",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Relatives have alleged that the head of the family who fell in Nainadivu and sustained serious head injuries, died due to the negligence of the Nainadivu District Hospital staff.",
        "This incident took place today, Sunday at 7.30 pm. In this incident, a father of 3 children named Chirambalam Selvakumar (age-42) of Nainadivu first district died.",
        "The head of the family, who had arrived in the passenger boat which arrived at Nainadivu Akuruthurai today at 6.30 pm, tripped and fell on his way home, sustaining serious injuries on his head.",
        "Relatives said that when he was immediately taken to the Nainadivu District Hospital, the staff there refused to admit him and told him to take him home and clean it up. Due to the delay, the head of the family died.",
        "On the other hand, the hospital officials said that due to the fact that the person was under the influence of alcohol, they could not give him proper treatment.",
        "Also, investigations have been started on the orders of the Director of Regional Health Services regarding the incident"
      ],
